{
  "stem": "19218.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But when they started bombing, everybody ran and everybody ran out of the factory.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I told him, I said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Kolojejchick, I cannot run without my brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He says, I cannot hide two people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I can hide one, but I can't hide two or it will be too suspicious and impossible.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I said, I thank you but I cannot run without him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I didn't, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I-- I-- I didn't know what the end will be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But the-- the desire to survive, the desire to avenge or revenge were so great that-- that-- that-- that-- that you do think.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You you, you-- you wanted to survive and number two is that you were always the number one in the camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You didn't care what happens to the other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I mean, you-- you-- once you allowed this to happen to you, of course, you were a goner, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Now, I don't know how we-- not me, but the Jewish people, the more learned ones, the rabbis, they knew when there was a Jewish holiday in there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Because even in the camps which didn't have anything to eat, but when it came the holy days, like Yom Kippur now, we were fasting.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We weren't even eating then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "So somehow, we knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Without a calendar, I don't know how the Jewish people knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But maybe they were marking off every day and we knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Anyway, of course, once we were inside the barracks, we would-- we could pray if we wanted to, but only if you knew it by heart.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I mean, there was nothing to pray from.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Now, the barracks, again, there were three tiers to sleep in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And at night you had a-- a-- a-- there was bucket in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
